{"tid":1828023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動PO】攬炒新年 !!","createTime":"2020-01-17T12:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T13:45:33.000Z","uid":198990,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e24df69ad24c5e6a6862450efc2036957fd26749","tid":1828023,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"由於上一篇文好似太曲 大家唔太睇得明  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1821510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1821510/page/1</a><br />\n今次就長話短說  直入重點<br />\n<br />\n文宣放呢度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RxvGYoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxvGYoW.jpg&h=de102551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0gGi0Cn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gGi0Cn.png&h=d59addc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShMKWaF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShMKWaF.jpg&h=fea3b8a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qg85FOL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqg85FOL.png&h=8b66f9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ejuc434.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjuc434.png&h=db691c2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>年三十 搶頭香活動 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n地點 : 黃大仙廟<br />\n時間 : 23 : 00<br />\n目標 : 攬炒新年 , 攬炒港豬 , 示威 , 公開既直播鏡頭<br />\n預期效果 : <br />\n大環境由於新年第一晚大型示威因素 , 令港豬往後幾日唔敢出街<br />\n造成經濟同消費意慾低迷 (每年新年 , 拜神賣香既鋪頭好好賺 一次夠捱成年) , <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">年初一  新春國際匯演</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n地點 : 西九文化區<br />\n時間 : 16 : 00 <br />\n目標 : <br />\n攬炒新年 , 攬炒港豬 , 示威 , 攬炒經濟 , 國際戰線 , 攬炒旅遊型像<br />\n對準政權活動 , <br />\n宣傳本港已被&quot;中國肺炎&quot;全面侵襲 , 建立&quot;沙士&quot;時期既風氣 <br />\n特別目標 : <span style=\"color: red;\">政府膠官</span> (車公廟) <br />\n19年 林鄭仲出席過花車巡遊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WcBNwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WcBNwH.png&h=b44cb201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預期效果 :<br />\n之前都話左19政府會取消煙花  <br />\n所以新年得番呢個大型公眾活動<br />\n政府花費<span style=\"color: red;\"> 4,200萬元</span> 搞呢個<strong>大白象工程</strong><br />\n舉行呢個新春國際匯演 , 預期令遊客全面地減入進入香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒旅遊業. </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對準膠官(政權) 要佢地自己親身面對市民<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">廢話 :</span><br />\n仲等咩?  同埋有唔少人都有潔癖話唔衛生<br />\n咁入境署放&quot;武漢肺炎帶菌者&quot;入境又好衛生?<br />\n2003年淨係一個沙士就經濟大破產<br />\n2020年&quot;武漢肺炎&quot;都唔會例外 , 加速攬炒<br />\n<br />\n本來攬炒就係焦土化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">放得人入境 就預左大規模爆發</span><br />\n附上 &quot;武漢&quot; 現況 蝗民微博截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xXx5dF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xXx5dF.jpg&h=33f78c49&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzrKWkm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzrKWkm.jpg&h=54fdf15f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozM69Fm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozM69Fm.jpg&h=13cfc4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>年初二  轉風車  附加祈福活動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n地點 : 車公廟  , 黃大仙廟<br />\n時間 : 10:00 am <br />\n目標 : <br />\n攬炒新年 , 攬炒港豬 , 示威 , 攬炒經濟 , 國際戰線 , 攬炒旅遊型像<br />\n特別目標 : <span style=\"color: red;\">政府膠官</span> (車公廟) <br />\n理由 : 由於過往咁多年同上年都有<span style=\"color: red;\">膠官</span>出席車公廟轉風車<br />\n所以特此推出呢行動 19年有葉瘤出席過 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahsBNr8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahsBNr8.png&h=b8ffbc08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預期效果 : <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒新年節目</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對準膠官(政權) 要佢地自己親身面對市民</span><br />\n平時你無機會見 大時大節終於黎<br />\n就算係替死鬼都好過無<br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">年初三   病變版 和理SHOP</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n時間 : 13 : 00<br />\n地點 : 廣東道 , 海港城 , 沙田新城市 , MOKO<br />\n目標 :  攬炒新年 , 攬炒港豬 , 示威 , 攬炒經濟 , <br />\n宣傳本港已被&quot;中國肺炎&quot;全面侵襲 , 建立&quot;沙士&quot;時期既風氣 <br />\n預期效果 : <br />\n攬炒經濟 ( 廣東道係全港最貴鋪租路段 ) , <br />\n攬炒港豬 , 驅散蝗民 還我淨土 . <br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n廢話時間 : <br />\n<br />\n和理SHOP唔係無成效 , 一定有 , 所以對家一定會極度重防 防止你咁做 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至濫權 , 濫捕 , 濫暴 都要阻止呢種合法而傷害極大既不合作運動.</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而且香港係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟社會</span></strong>, <br />\n只要動搖到呢個<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">根基 </span></strong><br />\n咁香港既<span style=\"color: red;\">社會架構就會被破壞</span><br />\n<br />\n立法會都係親商 , <br />\n所以商界一定係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">春袋</span></span></strong><br />\n商界講一句 政府就要收皮<br />\n<br />\n而且政府既最大收入來源係  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">稅!</span></strong></span><br />\n只要班商家佬無錢賺  賺唔到錢甚至蝕錢<br />\n佢地就唔洗<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">交稅</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁政府既國庫又會少左錢  班狗OT又億億聲<br />\n香港庫防 呢個春袋只要持續咁樣受衝擊<br />\n有朝一日就會乾塘  <br />\n到時就<span style=\"color: red;\">無錢出糧</span>俾班狗<br />\n更<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">莫講加人工   </span><br />\n<br />\n到時就可以期待<span style=\"color: red;\">政變同大罷工潮</span>既出現<br />\n<br />\n經濟抗爭行動一定要持續 唔可以停<br />\n<br />\nSUCK channel : <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=bfbf75b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n原PO : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1827997/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1827997/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新年我要攬炒 </span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a2e658a2b43f6e7503b9994ace1aceec3d86dd","tid":1828023,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"新年我要攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a664413ed49347fbb8ca1cd041fd74f62ffc40ff","tid":1828023,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:24:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新年我要攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"355d451958f96dfebff84f8fdd25d39caeb5d4ae","tid":1828023,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f004f2b89aecf10b41a6a8618002621ce692aedc","tid":1828023,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134006c920acc5ef58715e7e1e3f0a0df408deca","tid":1828023,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646478d297a103f218c241151c43f875882d2e64","tid":1828023,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-